            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Please see https://github.com/vim/vim/commit/b29f4abcd4b3382fa746edd1d0562b7b48c9de60#r144920264\n\n- `buf_set_name()` calls `fname_expand()`.\n- `fname_expand()` assigns `*sfname = *ffname` and `*ffname = fix_fname(*ffname)`.\n- `fix_fname()` returns either a newly-allocated string or `NULL`, so `*sfname` and `*ffname` must be different now.",
